{"tid":1225858,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1977年警廉衝突 總督麥理浩特赦所有之前涉貪未被檢控的警員","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:07:38.000Z","uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a087e8b60d32f23000d28130e92ba7601be6f11","tid":1225858,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考慮到大局及社會的反應後，麥理浩於同年11月5日決定對過去幾乎全部個案所涉及的大部分小規模貪污事件發出局部特赦令，指令總督特派廉政專員公署除了已經被審問、正被通緝和身在海外的人士，特赦於1977年1月1日以前所有涉嫌貪污而未被檢控的公職人員[5]。於同月7日，他向立法局強調有關特赦令只此一次，下不為例，表明不會再作任何讓步，同時，立法局又修改《警隊條例》，授予警務處處長權力，可以即時革除任何不服從《警察通令》和廉政公署條例的警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%AD%A6%E5%BB%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25BB%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdTFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=40883287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%AD%A6%E5%BB%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81</a>"},{"pid":"e9c0f00ac6308b7f3add1b2bcbf8bc7a76b63907","tid":1225858,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7d57695159ca390554f020c31eaf0da7150dda3","tid":1225858,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92502ee649e456cfe39918c8c5a8a047ff7c3552","tid":1225858,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22112e000d5f81cd53520e3ce6fff7025f53d6a","tid":1225858,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"以史為鑑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"